{"id":35421,"date":"2024-01-24T01:38:00","date_gmt":"2022-06-23T20:08:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=35421"},"modified":"2023-03-31T15:29:53","modified_gmt":"2023-03-31T09:59:53","slug":"bedroom-pastel-colors","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/bedroom-pastel-colors\/","title":{"rendered":"12 Pastel Bedroom Ideas You Will Want To Copy Now"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Here\u2019s your guide to making pops of pastel colours the language of your dreamy bedroom!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Pastel shades are gaining popularity recently because of their tranquil vibe and soothing appeal. These colour palettes make your bedroom look spacious, have a calming effect on your mind, and are Vastu-approved too, making them perfect for bedroom interiors. The ample white mix in pastel colours makes the space look tranquil yet maintains the colourful personality and vibrant aura that cheers you up every time you enter your room.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>So, get ready to revive your sleep cycle and enjoy a relaxing bedtime experience with these trendy pastel colour bedroom ideas. We bet you cannot resist replicating them in your home right away. Without further ado, let&#8217;s get started with some popular pastel bedroom colour schemes for you.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Pastel Blue Bedroom Perfect For Your Munchkin<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Blue is a soothing colour that adds to the playfulness of your kids\u2019 room. This <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/kids-bedroom-design\/\">kids\u2019 bedroom<\/a> in Sumadhara Nandanam, Bengaluru, is designed in an all-blue colour scheme for a vibrant look. The textured wall paint colour matches the wardrobe laminate beautifully. Meanwhile, the white headboard and side table break the monotony and bring an aesthetic balance. We also added a study unit with box cabinets matching the wardrobe to maintain continuity. This pastel blue bedroom is all you need to bring a smile to your kid&#8217;s face.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/27020944\/blue-bedroom-pastel-colors-perfect-for-your-munchkin-sumandhara-nandanam.jpg\" alt=\"Blue bedroom pastel colors perfect for your munchkin sumandhara nandanam\" class=\"wp-image-35422\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/27020944\/blue-bedroom-pastel-colors-perfect-for-your-munchkin-sumandhara-nandanam.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/27020944\/blue-bedroom-pastel-colors-perfect-for-your-munchkin-sumandhara-nandanam-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/27020944\/blue-bedroom-pastel-colors-perfect-for-your-munchkin-sumandhara-nandanam-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/27020944\/blue-bedroom-pastel-colors-perfect-for-your-munchkin-sumandhara-nandanam-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>An all-blue bedroom we designed for a client<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Pastel Yellow Bedroom Ideas For Guests<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Infuse a splash of spring into your guest bedroom with a pastel yellow accent wall. Take for example this guest bedroom that our experts designed in a home at Assetz 63 Degree East in Bengaluru. You can accentuate the space with an extended headboard in pistachio green and white. The wardrobe in wood-like laminates has ample storage space. The small study setup adds functionality and turns the room into a comfortable home office or kid&#8217;s study when guests aren\u2019t around.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/27021212\/yellow-pastel-bedroom-ideas-for-guests-assetz-93-degree.jpg\" alt=\"Yellow pastel bedroom ideas for guests assetz 93 degree\" class=\"wp-image-35423\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/27021212\/yellow-pastel-bedroom-ideas-for-guests-assetz-93-degree.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/27021212\/yellow-pastel-bedroom-ideas-for-guests-assetz-93-degree-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/27021212\/yellow-pastel-bedroom-ideas-for-guests-assetz-93-degree-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/27021212\/yellow-pastel-bedroom-ideas-for-guests-assetz-93-degree-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>A pastel yellow guest bedroom by Design Cafe<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Dual Shades For His And Her Section In The Kids\u2019 Room<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Our team designed this bedroom in Mumbai\u2019s Crescent Bay to cater to both the kids of our clients. The headboards in blue and pink demarcate their spaces beautifully. The study table with a wall-mounted storage unit helps them study with full concentration. We added an anti-skid rug on the floor to avoid accidents and add comfort. This dual pastel colour bedroom idea will come in handy for families with two kids.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/27021350\/bedroom-pastel-colors-with-dual-shades-for-his-and-her-section-in-kids-room-crescent-bay.jpg\" alt=\"Bedroom pastel colors with dual shades for his and her section in kids room crescent bay\" class=\"wp-image-35424\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/27021350\/bedroom-pastel-colors-with-dual-shades-for-his-and-her-section-in-kids-room-crescent-bay.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-cont